Boil the @milk{240%ml} and the @cream{360%g} with the @sugar{60%g}.

Pour over the egg mixture while whisking.

Skim the foam.

Add the @piment d'Espelette{1%tea spoon}.

Pour 14 cl of the mixture into 6 dishes of 12 cm diameter.

Bake in the oven at 120Â°C for ~{25%minutes} until the cream is firm to the touch.

